<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>Privacy Policy | Global Tip Calculator</title>
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
    <style>
      body {
        min-height: 100vh;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(120deg, #38bdf8 0%, #34b3a0 60%, #a78bfa 100%);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }
      .privacy-card {
        background: #fff;
        border-radius: 1.5em;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(52,179,160,0.13), 0 1.5px 8px rgba(52,179,160,0.07);
        padding: 2.5em 2em 2em 2em;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 3vh auto;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
      }
      .privacy-card h1 {
        font-size: 2em;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #34b3a0;
        margin-bottom: 0.7em;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .privacy-card ul {
        padding-left: 1.2em;
        margin-bottom: 1.5em;
      }
      .privacy-card li {
        margin-bottom: 1em;
        font-size: 1.08em;
        color: #23272f;
      }
      .privacy-card p, .privacy-card a {
        font-size: 1.08em;
        color: #23272f;
        text-align: left;
      }
      .privacy-card a {
        color: #34b3a0;
        text-decoration: underline;
        font-weight: 500;
      }
      .privacy-card a:hover {
        color: #38bdf8;
      }
      @media (max-width: 700px) {
        .privacy-card {
          max-width: 98vw;
          padding: 1.2em 0.5em 1em 0.5em;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="privacy-card">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p>At Global Tip Calculator, we value your privacy. Here is how we collect, use, and protect your information:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Cookies and similar technologies:</strong> We use our own and third-party cookies (such as Google AdSense) to display personalized ads, analyze traffic, and improve user experience.</li>
